6:
They're still going? They've been
working for so long...
10:
Indeed. Liesel is a potent cleric, but
her stamina isn't infinite. She's really
overworking herself.
13:
Her heart really seems to be in it,
though.
19:
Liesel, would you like to take a break
with me?
30:
That's right! I think you're overdue for
some relaxation—we'll be borrowing
you for... say, a day!
34:
A whole day? But I still have so much
work to do...
43:
That's right! We heard about this
place from Marina—she gave it a
raving review. Look how much they
have on the menu!
45:
Just some bread and water will be
more than enough for me!
48:
I'm not sure they sell bread and
water at an ice cream stand.
58:
Cheese flavored ice cream? I...
guess that could work? They've got
honey and cream cheese too!
60:
Oh, but the fruit flavored one sounds
good too. So... hard... to choose...
67:
Why don't we all buy something
different and then try a bite of each
others' ice cream, just to compare?
71:
That sounds like a good idea! Let's
go with that!
95:
Oh man, I haven't had a brain freeze
in so long. That was actually kinda
nostalgic.
97:
Yes, it was like I was a young child
again.
103:
You often ate ice cream when you
were younger?
107:
Yes, and I would get brain freezes—I
remember mother and father gently
laughing at me every time.
110:
I'm sure that this, too, was the
guidance of the Stars!
112:
If it be the will of the Stars, I'll make
sure to eat even more ice cream
from now!
126:
This is... enjoyable.
Eating ice cream is really fun.
128:
Of course! Once you dig in, it's hard
to stop yourself!
132:
Make sure you don't overeat and get
yourselves sick, though!
Okay, where to next?
135:
I'd like to go swimming! I've been
staring at the sea this whole time
without getting my feet wet!
138:
Sounds great, let's go! Don't forget to
bring sunscreen!
144:
That was so fun! I can't remember
the last time I got to enjoy myself
like this.
147:
A whole day just went by in the blink
of an eye!
151:
Those guys spent the entire day
working, overjoyed that their
Guardian Angel was out having a
good time.
155:
They're such hard workers... I'll have
to help them out again later!
160:
Let's go out on the town again
sometime soon.
166:
Oh, I bet if my master could see this,
he'd be smiling from ear to ear!
177:
I had specific instructions from my
master...
To fall in love!
185:
Love!
He said that before I begin my
training, I should go and fall in love!
187:
The fun I felt today—maybe that's
brought me one step closer to
understanding what love is? I'm not
sure.
188:
Would you be my guide? Help me
understand love?
194: Do you know how to help, Alk?
200:
Huh? Um, I'm not really sure that's
something you can teach...
203:
You know what? Light is probably
the person to ask about this! He's
got way more life experience than
us!
210:
Wh-what?!
Don't bring me into this!
216:
Please tell me, Champion. What is
love?
